{
  "stem": "7358.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she also used to-- she played the violin, and so she took extra lessons for that.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister's name was Chava.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my younger sister's name was Esther.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was three years younger than myself.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my older sister was three years older.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was born in May 15, 1928.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was-- it was-- most of the population were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was approximately 2,000 inhabitants at the time, and maybe 150 non-Jewish people, Polish-- mostly Polish and-- and some Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The area was inhabited mostly by Ukrainian people, the surrounding area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Polish people used to be encouraged by the Polish government to come and settle between the Ukrainians, so the Polish government would have sort of a foothold in the general area.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So between the Ukrainian villages here and there, there were Polish villages, which the government used to subsidize and encourage to settle.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That in itself did not affect the Jewish community.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believe, to the best of my knowledge, that we got along better with the Polish people, only because they were a minority between the Ukrainians.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were a minority, of course.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So, sort of, we were friends of necessity.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In-- in-- in 1938, in 1939, we began to-- to sort of get-- get the information in the papers that bad things are happening in Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was difficult for us to even imagine to what extent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were removed from-- there was very poor communication.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We lived far away from a major city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a local newspaper that used to just reprint some information, so we really were not very well-informed until much later.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Later on in 1939, it became-- everybody was aware that things are bad.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
